msgid ""
"<1.so>Thunder sure is scary, isn't it?<2.pa>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Speaking of! Have you heard the story,\n"
"buddy?<3.pa> Some say that rumbling sound\n"
"is the angry ranting of a dragon god!\n"
"But who knows if that's even true.<4.pa>\n"
"I've certainly never seen any proof!"
